summary: AN ORDINANCE adopting the findings of the City Council Committee of the Whole made following a public hearing pursuant to Resolution 23812 and in connection therewith ordering the designation of certain portions of Delridge Way Southwest, \*\*\*\*, Duwamish Avenue South, South Spokane Street and all or certain portions of the real property abutting upon each such street as part of a limited access highway facility. (West Seattle Freeway, Phase I)
